      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this reliable daily driver! It's a solid vehicle that has served its previous owners well and still has plenty of life left in it. While it shows some honest wear and tear both inside and out, and will eventually need some routine maintenance and minor repairs, it remains a functional and dependable choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation. This is a great opportunity to own a sturdy car with a lot of heart!",
