    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a dependable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches on the passenger doors and some paint oxidation on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and the transmission shifts as it should, though the next owner should anticipate replacing the brake pads within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for functional transportation at a reasonable price point.",
