      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in pristine, showroom condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an uncompromising exterior finish and a meticulously maintained interior that reflects a history of stringent, climate-controlled care. For the discerning collector who demands automotive excellence and mechanical integrity, this offering stands as a quintessential example of the model's finest form.",
